TEXT
${font monospace:size=20} $alignr ${time %l:%M:%S %p}${font monospace:size=9}
$alignr ${time %A %B %d}

TILING KEYBINDS ${hr 2}
S+u $alignr Focus North
S+n $alignr Focus South
S+j $alignr Focus West
S+k $alignr Focus East
S+a $alignr Toggle Maximize
S+h $alignr Toggle Horizontal
S+v $alignr Toggle Vertical
S+Sh+j $alignr Snap <--
S+Sh+k $alignr Snap -->
S+c $alignr Move to Center
S+Up $alignr Move North
S+Down $alignr Move South
S+Left $alignr Move West
S+Right $alignr Move East
S+Sh+Up $alignr Resize North
S+Sh+Down $alignr Resize South
S+Sh+Left $alignr Resize West
S+Sh+Right $alignr Resize East
S+z $alignr Desktop Keybinds
